{"tid":1365812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出發前記住記住","createTime":"2019-07-25T18:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T18:47:20.000Z","uid":55475,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb167ad81a5664fe00e03a1fedba3abb15bd880","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:11:10.000Z","msg":"出發前同身邊人信得過既人講定去做咩 <br />\n例如wtsapp你老母 講定只係打算去元朗食糖水<br />\n<br />\n總之要有record留得低<br />\n動機好緊要 有咩事隨時救你一命 <br />\n<br />\n所以記住出發前要有交帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063a515573119a9feee7754f88bf5404950ad1f0","tid":1365812,"uid":137053,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:12:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家真係要自己預備好需要嘅裝備啊，唔好成日發夢都靠現場有人俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如基本裝：頭盔、眼罩、豬咀<br />\n<br />\n用完又隨手抌咗佢，次次發完夢都見到有啲好新淨嘅裝被丟，好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多個為香港仆心仆命嘅香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f6ac8ff2c8a5acaa308b94d17147a11d457ffc","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56c22630f56c4be05e615a16e4db667810dfb64","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b95d2a9f87ac617d0e999733cfe83038a7d093","tid":1365812,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:15:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d82eddeddb90bd19ad3dda141084fdc9d814d681","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629b85d1f59a224f4e0e730ea252098b682b900e","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c792907ed33bbbeb3288f247c5d21ee2397b877b","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:20:36.000Z","msg":"做返個有交帶既人"},{"pid":"2490ed278ed4031d121f591c835e5a3af7f77134","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd24a05f8888b7647b98809d6ccb2629c7514a5","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:23:51.000Z","msg":"廢事比人誤會"},{"pid":"7480ebf734d0534118e03e210eb1fdcccea4915a","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449484db07f5aa5c6913eb5afedddc065498a59b","tid":1365812,"uid":265354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:27:15.000Z","msg":"法律上有用？<br />\n唔係好明🙌🏿"},{"pid":"2ec442cacbe17555344f0033d57bd6aa7b689c57","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca162d9d3808d27b88f257858cec29d275d00ad","tid":1365812,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 